title: Certificate of Proficiency in English E-books
description:
A collection of books hopefully useful to all students who strive to pass the Certificate of Proficiency in English tests.

Contains:

- Cambridge CPE - Certificate of Proficiency in English 1
- Cambridge CPE - Certificate of Proficiency in English 2 (+ audio)
- Longman - Grammar and Vocabulary for Cambridge Advanced and Proficiency
- Oxford University Press - CPE Practice Tests
- CPE Use of English 1 (students book + key)
